{
  "id": "1a4bdd50d62352d9",
  "fields": {
    "apply_url": "https://jobs.ashbyhq.com/skelar/76d11aee-8962-4725-9228-8fba8faa1808/application",
    "company": "skelar",
    "compensation": "",
    "content_hash": "1a4bdd50d62352d9",
    "department": "Backend",
    "description": "[https://app.ashbyhq.com/api/images/user-content/586ac3cb-f234-40cf-96fd-3daae8c41309/3a2721ac-0cf6-4bb5-a785-483b8d1018c3/Ashby_header.png]\n\nWho are we, and what do we aspire to?\nLiven is a product company that builds a companion for self-discovery.\nWe believe that self-discovery is a lifelong journey and want to help people navigate it every step of the way. That’s why Liven is building a system of tools to help people compose themselves and grow into who they want to become.\nPeople use Liven to track their mood, process emotions, and untangle thoughts by chatting with an AI companion. They build new routines with a task planner, explore how their brain and body react to trauma through personalized courses, take well-being quizzes, and relax or refocus with soundscapes.\nOur goal is to become the most trusted self-discovery companion globally. Liven is here to define and lead the mental wellbeing category. We aim to earn global trust by building an ecosystem of context-aware products for self-care and improvement. Our brand is optimistic and whimsical, yet wise and practical. We’re Liven! We bring joy back to life!\n\nWhat will you enjoy most about being on the Liven team?\nSince 2023, we’ve been scaling non-stop. We’re expanding the product, the team behind it, and our global reach. Liven has grown a lot since it was just a team of four. But our priority remains the same: building a vibrant culture where we share ideas, speedrun through challenges, and shape the business together.\n\nThe Role You’ll Own Senior/Lead Backend Engineer\n\n - Owning backend development within the product domain and actively shaping technical decisions\n\n - Working closely with stakeholders to turn business needs into practical, well-designed solutions\n\n - Setting a high bar for code quality and encouraging best engineering practices in everyday work\n\n - Collaborating with cross-functional teams to improve system integration and make processes smoother\n\n - Continuously evolving the codebase, architecture, services, and development practices\n\n - Leading, mentoring, and coordinating the backend development team\n\nPreferred Experience:\n\n - 5+ years of hands-on backend development experience\n\n - Experience in people management, with a genuine interest in growing and supporting a team (will be a plus)\n\n - Strong communication skills and the ability to work effectively with both technical and non-technical stakeholders\n\n - Ability to work within a dynamic environment\n\nOur Stack:\n\nNode.Js, Nest.js, Typescript, Postgres, Redis, Mongodb, BigQuery, GCP\n\nWhy Liven?\nPeople join Liven to bring to life the aspirations they once only dared to imagine.\nHere’s what we offer to support you personally and professionally while you grow with us:\n— A culture that values your ideas and empowers initiative.\n— A growing team of over 150 passionate professionals.\n— Health insurance, in-house doctor, and massage therapy.\n— Internal professional clubs on marketing, development, payments, customer experience, and entrepreneurship.\n— Sports and passion clubs: functional training, stretching, yoga, running, board games and more.\n— Opportunities for continuous learning and growth.\n— Meaningful work that makes a real impact.We also fund projects that help overcome the consequences of the war and contribute to Ukraine’s recovery through the SKELAR foundation, a charity created and run by our employees.\nIf you want to shape a product that helps people face challenges, process emotions, heal from trauma, rebuild a positive self-image, and rediscover joy — Liven is the place for you!\n\n[https://app.ashbyhq.com/api/images/user-content/586ac3cb-f234-40cf-96fd-3daae8c41309/bf8afb62-59f5-436b-b500-74f06bd0bb6e/Ashby_footer_eng.png]",
